119.name: Smart Dry Pedicure (no polish)
119.description:
Introducing Smart Dry Pedicure, the latest innovation in foot care! This revolutionary pedicure eliminates the need for water, using motorized discs called pododiscs to effortlessly buff feet smooth and soft.
Why choose Smart Dry Pedicure over traditional methods?
Enhanced exfoliation: Motorized pododiscs provide deeper exfoliation for incredibly smooth feet.
Sanitary: Single-use attachments prevent bacterial spread, and pododiscs are sterilized between clients.
Precision: Technicians expertly target trouble spots with adjustable pododisc speed and direction.
Customized: Abrasiveness levels are tailored to each client's needs.
Comfort: Pododiscs maintain an ideal temperature and avoid skin damage.
Hydration: Smart oils nourish and condition the skin during filing, resulting in renewed feet.
Long-lasting results: Smart oils seal smooth filing results, preventing rapid re-roughness and prolonging polish durability.
Ideal for those with calluses, cracked heels, ingrown nails, excessive sweating, or diabetic feet, Smart Dry Pedicure offers fast and transformative results. With regular sessions, you'll enjoy gorgeous feet all year round, making it an ultimate experience for everyone!
